REHEARING DOCKET

87-155. Carney v. McAfee.

Erie County, No. E-85-58. Reported at 68 Ohio St.3d 1416, 624 N.E.2d 191. On motion for rehearing or for clarification. Motion denied.

AW. Sweeney, Douglas and Pfeifer, JJ., concur. Wright, J., dissents. F.E. Sweeney, J., dissents and would grant sixty days for discovery. Moyer, C.J., and Resnick, J., not participating.
